StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetMostCurrentIST]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@NwaRowGuid uniqueiden..er
AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT Top 1 ID ,ProspectID ,TestDate ,Height ,Weight ,RunTimeMinute ,RunTimeSecond ,PuHang ,Crunch ,Pullup ,Pushup ,PlankMinute ,PlankSecond ,USMC.GetWeightPctOver(ProspectID, Height, 5) As OverMaxWgt5Pct ,USMC.GetWeightPctOver(ProspectID, Height, 10) As OverMaxWgt10Pct
FROM USMC.ProspectPhysicalIst WHERE ProspectID = ( SELECT ProspectId FROM usmc.Prospect WHERE NwaId = @NwaRowGuid ) AND (RunTimeMinute IS NOT NULL OR PuHang IS NOT NULL OR Crunch IS NOT NULL OR Pushup IS NOT NULL OR Pullup IS NOT NULL) ORDER BY TestDate DESC
END
